Reviews.Title: Great Adapter!
Reviews.Author: C. Davis
Reviews.Content: This unit is a replacement for a power supply that came from Korea. It is lower profile and works perfectly for what I need it for. Lightweight,one spot on an AC strip, and regulated. Excellent product!

Reviews.Title: Power!!
Reviews.Author: Danny J. Morton Jr.
Reviews.Content: I have Purchased 5 of these babies for my video equiptment needs , it runs perfect , it is small compact and sturdy enough to do some serious power supplies , would def. get more of these in future thanks Videosecu!!

Reviews.Title: Great power supply
Reviews.Author: Aaron Saks
Reviews.Content: Purchased 3 of these.  I used this power supply to power a Panasonic WJ-GXE500 CCTV network video encoder.  I cut the end off and used a meter to figure out which end was +.  The wire with the - - - - printed on it is positive/+.The power supply is Motorola branded, and has a red LED on the front of it when it is plugged in and has power.Works great!!!

Reviews.Title: Cheap, Light Weight and Does What It Needs to Do.
Reviews.Author: Free from Wires
Reviews.Content: Light weight and provided the power needed.I needed to reverse the polarity for my application, and by doing it myself saved a bundle.No more heavy wall transformers.

Reviews.Title: perfect for CPU fan
Reviews.Author: Koozi Guy "-Guy-"
Reviews.Content: I was in the middle of a home-made cat litterbox odor vent, and wanted to use a spare PC fan to blow the stank out. I snipped off the end of this 12V DC adapter, stripped the wires, twisted them to my stripped computer fan wires and closed them off with electrical tape (it was all I had on me at the time). Immediate success! Great reliable product, even with my poor workmanship.

Reviews.Title: Works great!
Reviews.Author: Jordan Runsvold
Reviews.Content: Used this power supply in an audio project. Disassembled and installed in a wireless microphone receiver. Works great and didn't introduce any noise into the system.

Reviews.Title: Works great so far.
Reviews.Author: John Redcorn "John Redcorn"
Reviews.Content: I'm using this to power a 5050 LED strip. It works just fine. Would buy again. The plugin portion can take up a few spots on a power strip depending on the orientation of the outlets on the power strip. I just switched power strips, problem solved. Have not used this for hours on end yet but I'm sure it will continue to perform as expected.

Reviews.Title: A must purchase for the IR illuminator
Reviews.Author: Kmill
Reviews.Content: Inexpensive and a must have for the IR illuminator. No issues with it at all. Plugs into a normal outlet and provides the juice needed.

Reviews.Title: Great little wart
Reviews.Author: P. L. Steele "snotbottom"
Reviews.Content: Puts out exactly what it says it will.  Nice and quiet too.  Was using a different wart for the transmitter on some wireless headphones and the noise was awful, with this unit it was not even noticeable.

Reviews.Title: Excellent power source and use as a regulator
Reviews.Author: Steve
Reviews.Content: I use these to power some equipment out in the field that require less than 500 ma and 12V. These work perfect, wrap up cleanly when not in use, are small in size, and have long cords.

Reviews.Title: Great replacement power supply.
Reviews.Author: D. Flowers
Reviews.Content: Needed to replace a week(cheap) power supply that came with a router.  This more than met the need.  It is of much better quality than what came with the router.  The router power supply would over heat and under volt the router causing it to lock up.  This transformer did not.  It dependable puts out rated milli-amps, with out any fuss!

Reviews.Title: Power to spare
Reviews.Author: Allen-the-not-so-wise
Reviews.Content: I was surprised that the power supply was interchangeable with the other cameras.Otherwise, some of the cameras could be picky about what power supplies they use.

Reviews.Title: VideoSecu 12V DC 500MA CCTV Camera Power Supply
Reviews.Author: Judy T
Reviews.Content: With this little jewel I was able to replace the failed AC adaptor on my wireless CCTV camera.The camera manufacturer wanted $20 for a replacement.I found this on Amazon for $8.I plugged it in and camera #1 was back on-line in no-time.I'm sure they all are made in the same factory in China anyway...

Reviews.Title: CAUTION
Reviews.Author: grandpairv
Reviews.Content: Caution only. No Complaint. However... when I tried to use this for a hobby project the draw was evidently slightly too high and burned this right out. There're a LOT of components in there!

Reviews.Title: Works perfectly at a great price
Reviews.Author: Chris B
Reviews.Content: I am using it with two QSee CCTV cameras and they have been working great for a few weeks now.

Reviews.Title: Clean and stable 12V power supply
Reviews.Author: F. Strecker
Reviews.Content: Small unit that delivers what it promises without overheating.  This allows it to be used in places with limited airflow.

Reviews.Title: Great Power Supply and Works Great with available cables
Reviews.Author: Texas Aggie
Reviews.Content: This Power Supply works great for our Daytime/Nightvision Camera that we use for a Day & Night Baby Monitor for our 2 year old Twins.  Instead of paying $130+ for an overpriced Fisher Price Audio/Video baby monitor that still has to plug into an A/C Electric Plug for the Transmitter which can kill a full grown adult, you don't want your baby/toddler touching those electric contacts and killing themselves either.  Use the 12 volt DC power supply for these cameras and plug it in from another room.  Works great!

Reviews.Title: VideoSecu AC/DC Power Adapter
Reviews.Author: L. mccarty "Mac"
Reviews.Content: Have three in use.  Very well built.  Slender style fits in a power strip very well.  A buy.

Reviews.Title: Works great for Arduino
Reviews.Author: Jacob Bates
Reviews.Content: I needed a 12v adapter to power my Arduino and some LED bars at the same time.  This worked perfectly.  The tip was the correct polarity and size.

Reviews.Title: A Great Product
Reviews.Author: Skidaddy22
Reviews.Content: This adapter works great. I love this adapter. I am overjoyed how this adapter works. Wow WOW wow wow wow

Reviews.Title: Bought for Linksys Wrt45G
Reviews.Author: jwang
Reviews.Content: I bought this ac adapter for my linksys wrt45g router. It matches and is so far so good.The price is OK, but still a little expensive. A 5 dollor should be a good deal.

Reviews.Title: Excellent general 12v supply fir home projects.
Reviews.Author: T or E. Helms
Reviews.Content: Excellent generic 12v power supply for home projects. I used this model to connect a wireless headphone system, normally for the car, into my home theater. Now I have 4 wireless headphones for big screen for less than 50 clams.

Reviews.Title: Works exactly as it should
Reviews.Author: TV-Tastic "Shawn"
Reviews.Content: I ordered a used TrendNet Wireless Gaming Adapter and the scammer on Amazon that sold it to me neglected to mention that the AC adapter was missing.  After arguing with me for two straight weeks over the issue instead of just taking care of it as a matter of customer service, the dope orders the wrong one and sends it to me despite the fact that I provided specifications and photos of the other AC adapter I had for my other wireless gaming adapter.  A quick search on Amazon for the specs I needed yielded this 12V DC 500mA Regulated CCTV Power Supply. The voltage and amps are exactly what my device needs and the design almost identical to the OEM power supply for the gaming adapter.  Works like a charm, no issues whatsoever and you can't beat the price.

Reviews.Title: Perfect solution for my camera
Reviews.Author: JD-ID
Reviews.Content: I have security cameras around my home.  One of them is on the far side of the house so I had to power it on that side of the house.  This works perfectly.

Reviews.Title: Small and compact
Reviews.Author: Jordan Germscheid
Reviews.Content: This worked great for what I needed it for. Small and compact.  Fits nicely in small spaces. Would buy again if I needed another.

Reviews.Title: Works as advertised
Reviews.Author: Ronald Freeman
Reviews.Content: It accomplished my needs just as advertised. I would recommend it to all. It was at a reasonable price and well designed. It solved my problem.

Reviews.Title: Works fine so far, doesn't cause as much interference as another brand
Reviews.Author: The Engineer Critic
Reviews.Content: This 12V power supply is regulated and doesn't cause as much RF interference as another brand I was using.  It doesn't have a power light, but I would still buy it again.

Reviews.Title: Good
Reviews.Author: jimbo
Reviews.Content: Have had two for six months and no problems so far. Put them on my security cameras and I'm happy

Reviews.Title: Power supply
Reviews.Author: Elwood Bishop
Reviews.Content: It worked for my Sentry wireless headphones but it had a very annoying buzz.  Could not use it.  Had to use my sons power supply.  Would not recommend it for use with the wireless headphones.

Reviews.Title: For Security camera
Reviews.Author: Cletu
Reviews.Content: I purchased this just to have an extra power supply for my security cameras, the price was right as well as the amperage.

Reviews.Title: Works Great
Reviews.Author: Ruso Minnifield "PrinceHappy2"
Reviews.Content: The VideoSecu 12V DC 500mA Regulated CCTV Camera Power Supply works good and the price was great.  I compared the price at another store and got this one a lot cheaper and it does a great job.

Reviews.Title: 1 year and still working
Reviews.Author: Peter Boyet
Reviews.Content: I ordered five of these to use with my wireless intercom units. this product simply works and is still working.

Reviews.Title: Works great for projects
Reviews.Author: Emi
Reviews.Content: Nice compact size and light.I needed a 12V DC 500mA power adapter to light the 11 LEDs in my arcade controller.Works great so far.

Reviews.Title: Works. Cheap.
Reviews.Author: C. Tin
Reviews.Content: I don't know what else to say about this adapter. I used it for a wireless music system and it's been working great. Nice and compact.

Reviews.Title: Bought 3 one gone
Reviews.Author: John E. Thomson "Doctorjet"
Reviews.Content: I bought 3 of these in September 3013 for my CCTV security cameras. One recently stopped working. I have since been told that a 500ma power supply has to work pretty hard to keep a CCTV camera going, therefore I have replaced it with a 1000ma power supply. So the fault is not necessarily that of the manufacturer. However, from now on I will buy 1000ma power supplies for my CCTV cameras.

Reviews.Title: Good Value
Reviews.Author: John F. Keith
Reviews.Content: Very good value and works well.  These are sometimes hard to find.  has been in service for 6 months and is still working well.  Good price.

Reviews.Title: works great
Reviews.Author: kcrocker
Reviews.Content: Works great and had no problems with it yet so far, It would of been better if it came with the camera.

Reviews.Title: VideoSecu 12V DC 500mA Regulated CCTV Camera Power Supply
Reviews.Author: Thomas P. Byrne Sr. "Thomas Byrne"
Reviews.Content: I needed a 12V DC 500mA power supply to replace one that broke. I found this unit, the ratings were a match, and the price was right. It has been in service 24/7 powering our weather warning device for the last couple of weeks and has worked flawlessly. I would recommend this product.

Reviews.Title: power supply
Reviews.Author: blanca
Reviews.Content: one more time I telling you this item is the complement for the mini camera I recommended buy the set  is just what every body needs the shipping was perfect and fast.

Reviews.Title: Not just cameras
Reviews.Author: AKA Joker
Reviews.Content: This worked perfectly for my Linksys WRT54G Router.  If you have a v5 or later of this router model then this power supply should work for you.

Reviews.Title: It's a power supply and it works
Reviews.Author: Mr. Pequod
Reviews.Content: There are companies out there selling security cams without the power supply. I got this one for a motion detector cam I bought earlier. It works great! Fast shipping too!

Reviews.Title: It Works
Reviews.Author: Angel Montanez Nazario
Reviews.Content: Nothing to wright  home about but that it gets the job done and is reasonably cheap and had to get it apart from the camera thaT NEEDS IT

Reviews.Title: VideoSecu 12V DC 500mA Regulated CCTV Camera Power Supply UL Listed...
Reviews.Author: M. Krawitz
Reviews.Content: This was good.  I got this to replace an adapter that was missing and this fit the bill.  Good adapter.

Reviews.Title: Perfect replacement Power supply for the Marsonic Noise Machine.
Reviews.Author: Perry
Reviews.Content: I, unfortunately burned out the original supply in Europe forgetting that 220 VAC is the norm, not 110 VAC as in the US and Canada.  Once I got back home, I checked the specs on the supply and bought this one as a replacement.  It worked just fine.It turned out that as a bonus, this was compatible as a switching supply, meaning it will sense any voltage automatically so it will work just fine on USA 110 and Europe 220 without a special transformer.  You will need an adapter because of the difference in the "prongs."

Reviews.Title: Power Supply
Reviews.Author: Victor V. Salvador
Reviews.Content: It works as advertised with this camera (Sony 3MM lens),cord is long enough to reach an outlet.It was included in the price.

Reviews.Title: FOR CCTV CAMERA NOT DVR
Reviews.Author: Southernboy
Reviews.Content: BOUGHT THIS FOR A SWANN DVR BUT IT WAS THE WRONG Ma .THE DVR REQUIRES 1000Ma OR HIGHER. THIS ADAPTER STILL POWERS THE CAMERA THOUGH.BEFORE PURCHASING CHECK OUTPUT Ma FIRST.

Reviews.Title: 12 V DC 500ma Power Supply
Reviews.Author: Anthony M. Wong
Reviews.Content: It did not work to my satisfaction.  All the specs were OK, but the unit would no stay on.  It would continuously cycle on and off at will.

Reviews.Title: Solid product
Reviews.Author: Dan
Reviews.Content: I purchased this as a replacement for the light for a wall clock.  It's been working for several months now with no problems whatsoever.  Shipped promptly and packaged well.

Reviews.Title: Good deal
Reviews.Author: Woodlandsman "Woodlandsman"
Reviews.Content: For a little more power to a pan and tilt camera, etc. this is a good bet in simple installations.

Reviews.Title: What can I say, it does what it is supposed to?
Reviews.Author: Anonymous "tapeworm"
Reviews.Content: I'm using these with the product ASIN: B000TBG8BU, and they work just fine. I wish the plug itself was a bit less bulky though.

Reviews.Title: Perfect for simple use.
Reviews.Author: Rolf Redford
Reviews.Content: I used it with micro tv and it worked just fine. Also as a bonus, 9 words for review minimum...

Reviews.Title: VideoSecu 12V DC
Reviews.Author: Charles W. McLamara
Reviews.Content: I had everything the Dvr,the BNC and then I found out I was missing the power necessary to operate the audio and video. The 12V Dc works never has failed me ,and I still have the origian power 12V Dc after about 1 1/2 years.Thank You

Reviews.Title: A Solid Performer At a Discount Price
Reviews.Author: MadCarpenter
Reviews.Content: I purchased this power supply to replace two energy hogging transformers that came with my LED aquarium 'moon lights'.It's not only more energy efficient than the two it replaced, it takes up less than half the space the other ones previously occupied on my power strip. And it shares the same size, type, and polarity of plug tip as my old transformers. With the addition of a couple of two-way splitter cables, it's able to power all three of my LED lighting units without even getting warm.It feels like a good deal for less than eight bucks.

Reviews.Title: good product
Reviews.Author: Tayls "Tayls"
Reviews.Content: good fast service and they work just fine.  I have had them installed for about a month now with no problems.  They work just like the orginals that came with my original package.

Reviews.Title: A shot in the dark hit the bullseye
Reviews.Author: Kenneth Kaplan
Reviews.Content: When the power supply for my multiple purpose portable "power station/air compressor" (AC/DC, air, jump starter, worklight) failed, I tried to match its specs, rather than its purpose. This works perfectly.

Reviews.Title: Good product, good price
Reviews.Author: Josh Leger
Reviews.Content: Cables are cables. They usually all work. And with Amazon, you will always find the best deals for the same quality.

Reviews.Title: Adequate power for most 12 volt cameras
Reviews.Author: Dr. Dave "Dr. Dave"
Reviews.Content: This product is well constructed with the best materials and excellent workmanship.This is a recommended product for you to purchase.

Reviews.Title: good
Reviews.Author: Bob "Bob."
Reviews.Content: powers my camera just like it should. ran the cord, plugged this into the wall and presto my camera magically worked?

Reviews.Title: Simply capable and powerful
Reviews.Author: LisaDawn McCabe "FuzzyRev"
Reviews.Content: These little powerhouses work beautifully with the Wireless Portable Intercom Voice Activated System that can also be used with batteries (only). I chose to use the add-on power supplies due to our system being on 24/7 - batteries can get very expensive!The 500mA capability works very well with our intercom system. Amazon.com claimed compatibility and that was correct. I do not hesitate to recommend them. The price was much better than what I would have paid locally and the construction is SOLID.

Reviews.Title: Works for my security cameras!
Reviews.Author: Chris S. Bizzelle
Reviews.Content: Theres not much to say about this, but I figured I'd at least mention it works for my cameras.  I had my house prewired with rg6 lines at the front and back doors, not knowing a lot about security camera systems I didnt think to prewire or plan a power source for the cameras.  So I'm still using the coax but these adapters make it easy to plug in to a nearby outlet.  The only thing I find odd is they get pretty warm, I know thats going to happen with adapters but this one felt a little warmer than usual.  I hope when they are in use in 100 degree weather they'll hold up.

Reviews.Title: Works, and a great price
Reviews.Author: J. Strickland
Reviews.Content: I have a long CCTV camera run and I used this AC adapter to power the camera locally, and used RG-59 cable with BNC connectors to carry the signal.  This is certainly cheaper than a 100 foot Siamese cable, and it works just fine.  It allowed me to use much tougher RG-59 cable for a long run that is going to get a lot of weather and mechanical stresses.  All in all, a good buy.

Reviews.Title: need it for security cameras
Reviews.Author: Gregory P. Stewart
Reviews.Content: If you're buying a camera by itself as opposed to buying a security dvr package, you'll probably need to purchase a seperate power supply. This is what you'll need to purchase. Works well.

Reviews.Title: Recommend!
Reviews.Author: Michael A., Davidson "Mike"
Reviews.Content: Service was good and product as described!  Just what I wanted and at the right price!

Reviews.Title: WORKS AS EXPECTED!
Reviews.Author: MR_BUYITNOW
Reviews.Content: I HAD NO PROBLEM WITH THIS .. IT POWERED UP MY MINI 3.5" MONITOR THAT I USE FOR A SECURITY CAMERA!! THANKS!!

Reviews.Title: Exactly as ordered
Reviews.Author: beardy
Reviews.Content: Received Power Supply by mail which could be easily put in my roadside boxin good time and a good product.

Reviews.Title: It's a power supply
Reviews.Author: GuidoTKP
Reviews.Content: What can I say?  It's the right tip size, tip polarity, and output for what I needed.  Works fine I suppose.

Reviews.Title: poor product
Reviews.Author: copperhead
Reviews.Content: I purchased several of these and every one of them blew their fuse which makes them useless. Just a poor product and cheaply made. i was using them to hook up a 9 light led strip which was within range of 12v adapter. Will not purchase anymore of these.
